# ── Build output (regenerated by PyInstaller from the .spec) ─────────────
/Pak-Rat.exe
/_internal/
/build/
/dist/
/_release/

# ── Release archives — host these as GitHub Release assets, not in-tree ──
*.zip

# ── Proprietary: Oodle is NEVER committed (RAD/Epic, non-redistributable) ─
# Everything else in vendor/ (repak, injector, texconv — all MIT/Apache) IS
# committed so this repo is the single clone-and-build source. Oodle is
# fetched on the user's own machine at first run; see core.ensure_oodle().
oo2core_*.dll

# ── Bulky generated data we don't ship in source ────────────────────────
Pak-Rat/data/assets.txt

# ── Python caches ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.eggs/

# ── PyInstaller intermediates ───────────────────────────────────────────
*.spec.bak
*.toc
*.pkg
warn-*.txt
xref-*.html

# ── Editor / OS cruft ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
